<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Nunito:400,600,700,800,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        
body {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;
  display:flex;
    justify-content: center;

}

img{
    width: 60%;
}

.main {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    width: 80%;
    height: 80%;
}

p {
    margin: 15px;
}

button {
    margin: 25px;
}

.code{
    padding:10px;
    background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    border-radius: 1px;
    font-size: 40px;
    letter-spacing: 10px;
}
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class ="main">
        <img src="https://i.ibb.co/wLRG8xX/Pilliz-logo.png" alt="Pilliz-logo"/>
        <p>
            Hi, <span id="name">&lt;{{name}}&gt;</span>
        </p>
        <p class="content">
            Thank you for registering with Pilliz.  To activate your Pilliz account, please verify your email by entering the code provided below.   
        </p>
        <p>
        Verification Code:
        </p>
        <p class = "code">
            {{code}}
        </p>
        <p class="content">
            If you are having trouble with this process, please let us know and we'll be happy to assist you further.
        <p class="content">
            Regards,
        <p>Pilliz</p>
    </div>
    </body>
</html>